column1: Courtney said "Eww like I would even align with you"
Russle said: "You think I wanna align with you? Im the king around here"
Randy said "Im old not stupid im not aligning with you"
Tyson said "Sure and while im at it why dont I just give you the million dollars"
Boston Rob said "Maybe we align  maybe we dontn just watch your back"
Coach said "Honor is the most important thing in this game  you havent shown me any"
Jerri said "Not a chance"
Sandra said "I wont promise you anything  just dont vote me out"
Parviti said " I am really not interested"
Danielle said "I dont think thats in my best interest now  maybe after the next tribal?"
Courtney said "Lets do it everyone else is a loser"
Russle said "The best decision you ever made was to align with me"
Randy said "I usually dont want help but I like you"
Tyson said " Sure, we can split the million too"
Boston Rob said "Just remember whos in charge here"
Coach said "You have proven your honor to the dragon slayer rise dragon born"
Jerri said "Sure! lets take this thing to the final three!"
Sandra said "I wont promise you anything just dont vote me out and I wont vote you out"
Parviti said "As long as you dont vote for me were solid"
Danielle said "Perfect timing! Lets do it"
Courtney said "Can you just shut up for like 5 minutes"
Russell said "Do not approach the king unless spoken too"
Randy said "You make me wish for death"
Tyson said "Oh wow your talking to me? I'm thrilled"
Boston Rob said "How about this you stop talking to me"
Coach said "Please leave me alone when I am meditating"
Jerri said "We really have nothing in common"
Sandra said "Listen I dont wanna hear your life story, just don’t vote me"
Parviti said "Wowww thats like sooo cool"
Danielle said "Do you bore yourself?"
Courtney said "Can you believe how dumb everyone here is?"
Russell said "Im the king and youll be my jester"
Randy said "I apperciate you saying that"
Tyson said "Okay you can hang sometines"
Boston Rob said "You know youre alright"
Coach said "Thank you for meditating with me"
Jerri said "Have we gotten close?"
Sandra said "Youre alright but I am not saying I trust you"
Parviti said "I guess your not the worst person here"
Danielle said "I am glad your still here"
Courtney said "Okay it is offical I hate you"
Russell said "If you come for the king you best not miss"
Randy said "You are the dumbest person on this island"
Tyson said "Big mistake pal"
Boston Rob said "Who do you think runs this island punk"
Coach "You are the Dragon and I must slay you"
Jerri said "The black widow is coming for you"
Sandra said "YOU WANNA GET LOUD! CAUSE I CAN GET LOUD TOO!"
Parviti said "I am not wasting anymore time with you"
Danielle said "What the FUCK did I do to you"
Courtney said "I know you want to talk but I just do not care right now"
Russle said "Can you not see I am a little busy we can talk later"
Randy said "Dont you take a hint"
Tyson said "I am practing my signature right now we can talk later"
Boston Rob said "We gotta work on the shelter bud no time to talk"
Coach said "In silence we find inner peace"
Jerri said "I will get back to you real soon"
Sandra said "Just do not vote for me and we will be square"
Parviti said " Haha.."
Danielle said "You kinda lost me there"
Marisa said" OOOO that a great idea"
Mike said "You and me ride or die"
Bety said "Now that is just the darndest idea I ever heard"
Ashley said "All the way honey"
Liz said "We can totally do this together"
Jaison said "Togther we will be unbeatable"
Mick said "Well that could work"
Ben said "Love it"
Russell said "I promise you final three"
Natalie said "I promise to be loyal to you"
Marisa said "Can we talk in a sec"
Mike said "I would rather fish than talk now"
Betsy "Right after I take a dip we can talk"
Ashley said "You worry to much"
Liz said "We can wait after this vote"
Jaison said "Lets see how the challenge goes"
Mick said "Is that the best idea right now"
Ben said "Maybe"
Russell said "Maybe I will take you to the final three"
Natalie said "Im sorry I cant promise anything right now"
Marisa said "I promise you are next"
Mike "You sure got a mouth"
Betsy "You are a bad person"
Ashley "Get out of my face"
Liz said "Nobody talks like that to me"
Jaison "Who taught you to run your mouth like that"
Mick said "Wow cannot believe you said thaty"
Ben said "Keep one eye open when your sleeping"
Russell said "Who do you think your talking too! Im the king"
Natalie said "I did not like that"
Marisa said "Youre a real treat you know that"
Mike said "I love you so much"
Betsy  said "Stop your making me blush"
Ashley said "You always make me smile"
Liz said "That means the world to me"
Jaison "Youre a beast around camp"
Mick said "I like having you around"
Ben said "Thanks for listening"
Russell said "Thanks"
Natalie said "Well now you got me smiling"
Marisa said "Thats not how you talk to me"
Mike said "Do you think when you speak"
Betsy said "Do not say something like that again okay"
Ashley said "Okay well you do not have to be rude"
Liz said "I know your mad but do not take it out on me"
Jaison said "You got an attitude"
Mick said "Please relax I can not take you anymore"
Ben said "NOW THATS ENOUGH"
Russell said "Who you callin fat"
Natalie said "Well I do not think that is actually true"
Marisa said "What did you mean by that"
Mike said "Ireally need to stretch before the challenge"
Betsy said "I am awful tired right now"
Ashley said "After I fix the shelter"
Liz said "I can barely hear you"
Jaison said "We cannot talk now I hear people coming"
Mick said "Huh thats interesting"
Ben said "Hmmm"
Russell said "Are you brain dead I am busy"
Natalie said "I would sure love to talk to you but I am awful busy honey"
